title: THE LUCKY LUX!

embed.description: Hello! Welcome to my first ever video! Got any ideas? Feel free to comment them! If you enjoyed please Like the video and Subscribe to support me! THE LUCKY LUX..? SCRIPTS.

body: Hello.. There is no reason as to why you should watch this Video, but most people tend to advertise their first few videos on Game Boards to gain recognition! Here is a montage i made with some clips i got the last few days, I tried to keep it normal, but i'm experimenting with Software and wanted to try out different techniques. Anyways, i'd love some feedback from you guys! (Hopefully it's not bad, but it'll do!)
